### **strapi-editorial-template**

```powershell
cd F:\project_workspace\strapi-editorial-template
# Phases 3–4 on main
# Phase 5 — if remote has release/v1.0.0 and prod uses it:
git checkout release/v1.0.0
git reset --hard main
git push origin release/v1.0.0
git checkout main
# Else: main is deploy branch — push main only
```

**Strapi secret extras:** never commit `.env`, Strapi admin JWT secrets, AWS keys in `config/plugins.ts` overrides, or `database/*.env`.

