## **Anti-patterns**

- ❌ Commit only `.cursor/rules/*` while `git status` shows other modified files
- ❌ Skip secret filename scan after `git add -A`
- ❌ Push feature branch only and assume Amplify/ECS prod deployed
- ❌ `git config http.sslVerify false` globally (use one-time `$env:GIT_SSL_NO_VERIFY`)
- ❌ Force-push `release/v1.0.0` without user approval

